174 A.3d 510 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. MICHAEL DERRY, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-192 September Term 2017

079395 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005674-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
